frus:attachment.p:
But the Government attorney might say: It is true that there is no rebellion;
                        it is true that those documents furnish no proof of the existence of one;
                        yet the conspiracy remains.

list.item:
Whereas it is proved that Don Julio Sanguily was arrested in the house
                            where he resided in this capital, at an early hour of the morning of
                            February 24, viz, the same day on which the uprising took place;
